            "title": "美股開市前，恐慌指數飆升12%！美指期貨齊升，原油飆升5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周一，4月20日，停火協議即將到期，第二輪談判懸而未決。美股開市前，CBOE Volatility Index飆升12%，美股指期貨集體下跌，納指100期貨跌0.46%，道指30期跌260點，跌幅達0.53%，標普500期貨跌0.44%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"192\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LQlm5.5bxB9S.e76qQUTcg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/469ef5bcfc6d30b63f78c67a504c8f0a\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">XAU/USD在4800美元附近徘徊，白銀跌1.64%報79.48美元。原油飆升5%，倫敦布倫特原油期貨現報94.96美元；WTI原油期貨現報87.22美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f3a8bdf1-8fb5-31b1-9ac3-172ff6a8138d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"672\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kjVV5g.EHIGnIei4o4qixw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExNDQ-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/146b8cdfb1047d4ab39254a9351b10a8\" width=\"564\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數升0.16%，現報98.26。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshma